            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Reading: The proposed reading is upwards from the broad end of the fragment. The first letter U is perhaps best understood as the remaining three strokes of an I (five strokes), and the T as three of the four strokes of a C. The resulting IMUC could then be what remains of the formula MAQI MUCOI. The less probable reading in the other direction results in ...VUMU..., which is less amenable to analysis and less likely due to the layout and shape of the fragment.</p>
            </div>
